        "test_pre_test_info": "\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003EIn our fast-paced urban lives, maintaining optimal health is often a challenge. The City Advanced Health Package is a comprehensive health screening program designed to provide individuals with a thorough assessment of their overall health. This package goes beyond the basics, delving into key indicators such as glucose fasting, HbA1c, KFT, RFT, lipid profile, and more.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EGlucose Fasting and HbA1c:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E\u003Ci\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EImportance:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/i\u003E Monitoring glucose levels is vital for detecting early signs of diabetes. Fasting glucose levels and HbA1c, which reflect average blood sugar levels over time, are crucial indicators in assessing diabetes risk.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E\u003Ci\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EBenefits:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/i\u003E Early detection allows for timely intervention and lifestyle modifications, reducing the risk of complications associated with diabetes.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EKFT (Kidney Function Test) and RFT (Renal Function Test):\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E\u003Ci\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EImportance:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/i\u003E The kidneys play a pivotal role in filtering waste and maintaining fluid balance. KFT and RFT assess the efficiency of kidney function, detecting potential issues such as kidney disease or dysfunction.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E\u003Ci\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EBenefits:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/i\u003E Early identification of kidney problems can lead to proactive management, preventing further deterioration and enhancing overall kidney health.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ELipid Profile:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E\u003Ci\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EImportance:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/i\u003E A lipid profile measures cholesterol levels, including LDL (low-density lipoprotein), HDL (high-density lipoprotein), and triglycerides. Abnormal lipid levels are linked to cardiovascular diseases.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E\u003Ci\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EBenefits:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/i\u003E Understanding lipid levels helps in formulating personalized strategies for managing heart health, including dietary changes and lifestyle modifications.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EComprehensive Blood Count (CBC):\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E\u003Ci\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EImportance:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/i\u003E CBC evaluates different blood components, providing insights into overall health and detecting disorders such as anemia, infections, and certain cancers.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E\u003Ci\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EBenefits:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/i\u003E Early detection of blood-related issues enables timely medical intervention, ensuring optimal blood health.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EThyroid Function Tests (TFT):\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E\u003Ci\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EImportance:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/i\u003E TFT assesses thyroid hormone levels, crucial for metabolism and overall well-being. Imbalances can lead to various health issues, including fatigue, weight changes, and mood disturbances.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E\u003Ci\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EBenefits:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/i\u003E Identifying thyroid dysfunction early allows for effective management, promoting energy levels and overall metabolic health.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E",
