        "test_pre_test_info": "\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003EIn a city where the pace of life is relentless, investing in one's health becomes paramount. The City Wellness Package emerges as a valuable tool in this endeavor, offering a thorough examination of key health markers. By opting for this comprehensive package, individuals can take proactive steps towards a healthier and more fulfilling life. After all, good health is not just the absence of illness but the holistic well-being of mind and body.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EGlucose Fasting Test:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E&nbsp;The City Wellness Package begins with a glucose fasting test, providing a crucial assessment of blood sugar levels after an overnight fast. Elevated blood sugar levels may indicate insulin resistance or diabetes, enabling early intervention and lifestyle modifications.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERoutine Urine Examination\u003C/strong\u003E:\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003EA routine urine examination is included to evaluate kidney function and detect any abnormalities such as proteinuria or hematuria. This test plays a vital role in identifying potential kidney issues at an early stage.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECBC with ESR (Complete Blood Count with Erythrocyte Sedimentation Rate):\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E&nbsp;This comprehensive blood test assesses red and white blood cell counts, hemoglobin levels, and platelet counts. Additionally, the erythrocyte sedimentation rate provides insights into inflammation within the body. A CBC with ESR aids in diagnosing a range of conditions, from anemia to infections.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EThyroid Stimulating Hormone (TSH) Test:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E&nbsp;The TSH test evaluates thyroid function by measuring the level of thyroid-stimulating hormone in the blood. An imbalance in thyroid hormones can lead to various health issues, including fatigue, weight fluctuations, and mood swings.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E",
