        "mrp": 1510,
        "no_of_parameters": 49,
        "offer_price": 599,
        "package_type": "health-package",
        "search_tag": "City Affordable Care Package",
        "specialityName": "City Affordable Care Package",
        "test_name": "City Affordable Care Package",
        "test_pre_test_info": "\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003EPrioritizing health through regular check-ups is a fundamental step towards a healthier and happier life. The City Affordable Care Package addresses the financial barriers associated with comprehensive health screenings, making it easier for individuals to take charge of their well-being. By including key tests such as cholesterol, creatinine, urea, and TSH, this package empowers individuals to monitor and manage their health effectively. Remember, investing in health today is an investment in a healthier future.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECholesterol Test:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003EHigh cholesterol levels are a significant risk factor for heart disease and stroke. The City Affordable Care Package includes a cholesterol test, measuring the levels of LDL (low-density lipoprotein) and HDL (high-density lipoprotein) cholesterol. Monitoring cholesterol levels can help individuals make informed lifestyle choices and reduce the risk of cardiovascular diseases.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECreatinine and Urea Tests:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003EKidney health is vital for overall well-being, and the City Affordable Care Package addresses this by including tests for creatinine and urea levels. Creatinine is a waste product produced by muscles, and elevated levels may indicate impaired kidney function. Urea, another waste product, is filtered by the kidneys, and abnormal levels can signal kidney problems. Regular monitoring of these parameters allows for early detection and intervention, promoting kidney health.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EThyroid-Stimulating Hormone (TSH) Test:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003EThe thyroid gland plays a crucial role in regulating metabolism through the production of hormones, with TSH being a key indicator. The City Affordable Care Package includes a TSH test to assess thyroid function. Imbalances in thyroid hormones can lead to various health issues, including fatigue, weight changes, and mood swings. Early detection through the TSH test enables prompt management and improves overall well-being.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E",
        "test_status": true,
        "test_url": "city-affordable-care-package",
        "updatedAt": "2024-02-27T05:27:39.849Z",
