        "test_components": "\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECholesterol, Total (1 Test):-\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:15px;\"\u003E Total Cholesterol\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECreatinine (1 Tests):-\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:15px;\"\u003E Creatinine\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EGlucose Fasting (1 Test):-\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:15px;\"\u003E Glucose Fasting/blood Sugar Fasting\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESGOT (AST) (1 Tests):-\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:15px;\"\u003E SGOT (AST)\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESGPT (ALT) (1 Tests):-\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:15px;\"\u003E SGPT (ALT)\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EUrea (1 Test):-\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:15px;\"\u003E Urea\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERoutine Urine Examination (17 Tests):-\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:15px;\"\u003E Colour, Transparency, Specific Gravity, PH, Urine Albumin, Ketones, Glucose, Leucocyte Esterase, Nitrite, Blood, Pus Cells, R.B.C, Casts, Crystals, Epithelial Cells, Yeast Cells, Others\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECBC, Complete Blood Count (25 Tests):- \u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:15px;\"\u003EHaemoglobin, TLC (Total Leucocyte Count), Neutrophil, Lymphocytes, Monocytes, Eosinophil, Basophils, RBC, PCV/Haematocrit, MCV, MCH, MCHC, Platelet Count, Absolute Neutrophil Count, Absolute Lymphocyte Count, Absolute Monocyte Count, Absolute Eosinophil Count, Absolute Basophil Count, RDW-CV, RDW SD, PDW, MPV, P-LCR, PCT, IG\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:16px;\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETSH (Ultra Sensitive) (1 Test):-\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:15px;\"\u003E TSH (Ultra Sensitive)\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E",
